            <span>‚ùì How to use this tool</span>
            <span class="help-toggle" onclick="toggleHelp()">[Hide/Show]</span>
        </h4>
        <div id="helpContent">
            <p><strong>1. Choose Type:</strong> Select "Goods" (physical items) or "Services" (time/labor) for each side.</p>
            <p><strong>2. Enter Base Value:</strong> For goods, enter the Fair Market Value (what it sells for used). For services, enter hourly rate.</p>
            <p><strong>3. Adjust Factors:</strong> Use the dropdowns to adjust for condition (Is it new?) and your desire (Do you really need it?).</p>
            <p><strong>4. Check the Meter:</strong> Click "Evaluate Trade" to see if the deal is balanced or if cash is needed to make it fair.</p>
